_chmod_ - change file mode (permissions)

_chmod_ *augo+-rwxst* *file1*...
_chmod_ *mode* *file1*...

 *a*     set/reset mode bits for everyone
 *u*     set/reset the owner's mode bits
 *g*     set/reset the group mode bits
 *o*     set/reset the other mode bits

 *+*     set the mode bits
 *-*     reset the mode bits

 *r*     set/reset the read permission bit
 *w*     set/reset the write permission bit
 *x*     set/reset the file execute/directory search permission bit
 *s*     set/reset the setuid/setgid bit
 *t*     set/reset the sticky bit

 *mode*  octal mode

 *file1*... files to change
